可以肯定的是，我们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbe0bd659d894c958b24044e1ae467ba&amp;amp;_e=vmU5GxOGhYA0OGjPUrAy3vtug7IDPN2nwEJh-pBzigLSbJdVxBz5WYvgbXA670y7U8A6BuanaEEI6V-5UKyo7wh1Scxva15yL9dSkjBPPTrDwYa-uSMN1BZWaUx0l0ZMchFfgXF-oNGoiM4sRhkyB2UaYU972nYGHFOTMN4lQCxk7_bqMFsfwT0uVmbekalmN4ITZBi-IxoUr5iBeV0deVubWybIfF5g3QTRzYb5VQ1yMYKJ51zPMp_uE5LkoZIORpgJ2xqPzEruJ8zF6roQ0VPyu-9B1ZOCizs3wVQbsD_O-2qgLS21p2oQBPT5t127TWIkmIjaSf8lAL2wnooysOK4vki12UND7fdaFS0J_T8zpIYB1dFODLwzWmYYd4GJULFRZkQt0B_6pfMKHt7_pteKtwOKimZtsnP-1Z345p55vVZo8kqhxyiAoQ4l7Lzh781-VymgwE6CUQWzA7XrNYh4ZR24WfaC6o2Gqq4J8CIqEbibW-q2Se10B-UfmOInzegJdZT_SubycxbnI0shg3XuLCH-3hoSnCiJJda0Pbzfd3vfGW90-zffIAPkC0puYxfm2WX808yFiKtQqP1WOIsFUWo9RQmW2aYUnHxjGEPvffusI0H7F0sNq2aA_nNCpJBipjqnsmLKF6UoLac4XoSDU6tR2lrIQkPkGu2UJLUOJRlNlVxkFVPh2gZNvI9dLfZeu0cMM3cmyUIosWsY1Rf2XXisCLulqJxZRP-wrMtjibIGOhpxF4ed6ZKRhKq0jeZ9xXfOSlBlJWspA4MZXo8jd1grJFkaG7XTrtTGvZ-60mfzYO-UKrrTChONCXyBlvT_VwRoJSnYrHwAfbHXpg%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="另一场流行病不可避免，但我们还没有准备好"&gt;没有为此投入应有的关注或资源&lt;/a&gt;。）&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;加密货币：它有什么好处？我应该拥有更多吗？&lt;/strong&gt;这是我们最喜欢的电子邮件之一：“我正在考虑加密货币。在我所有的研究中，我没有找到令人信服的理由去拥有它，但我确实这么做了。” （ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbe0bd659d894c958b24044e1ae467ba&amp;amp;_e=vmU5GxOGhYA0OGjPUrAy3vtug7IDPN2nwEJh-pBzigKFrFJXAaeDfJrpfbjuklCn5DETbI3nn8AGTVCVxiSQTsoGx1YOstFwhppE_nYw51kKUgTPaLcAxJRkm2lYnyTJ1K6PFWRQtN2YEdtSj7DCbIlHcK5nqY6IHTUZ6wadZv-labvzuR2hz6M-kFhR6tQhZuXdYL_g4bSVpL5KcMAwjAxunfXBw9npYFPV3LSRYECa0NFGDHYtvsnn8DpoIhsDaU6d8KP8WbzIbD1sYsi1Booo3kGTUO2HyGdDorGAsvSks2rNHmYS7OaspgzeGKJgM7R13CLTuzvU96zdhtRjX6t4Wu-DxpWUycpNATwrPVg28us8oONB-C2ghbfDBKvtzKwuNrJK8nxNb0022gMHL31ipAH1fCK1lwHesBDnseTLuTumUG4qg4Giv93Yhp_ElP7kpq4WSpECW5vo_TKktq02JZu15e_J9q4UPtqlz_Z_ZuhbXD61BPqvvM1G-wISHPpyi4h6Y2zp7gFz6mo9ZaQ2s