KYF0ciNl3CHGYNTixZ3uzJ4gOqfE7Jz4mSEuFaU" target="_blank"&gt;科学争论&lt;/a&gt;。随着世界变暖，风会变得更强还是更弱、更频繁还是更少，这些都存在不确定性。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=1b20d78946fe438a9ac466a4e85f1974&amp;amp;_e=PU2eBGaYg-XqhBpqH_rEUBtsuT3l4h6xBXd6rQ1RDLIaAVm5XaZvtrxO4M3BMU_eHEUv-bndhLX4CV3yl4EPJ-VdU0RlELiim4baIymwO0hWbgRpiN88jxy1cKsJnpnTcnIsUHzbwHU7DSdSN4VpE258jrYHIAspQJ1c-ZKZer2JB1gIab7U2QoEes5bUyiqzx5L3DdysxdL6QY-qnm6hbhqyu20ihbmj9oqx4l7AnsWb-AYWhChpWYnRWv0xZgoznYonZ5__3S9Nc7rYpVdNb1TiehGY1y775ycucbmUzk2QmgIH2dsQx1p5GDdDce-1hYNCM625HxLFxhDkd_yahN3IHY97WHzlKp33NLFfS3cFwOW7iyl965Y25bW3HIsRLMyrAP0bovxRkI1135CfNs7evf1_WxzEAyWDeS94Mp11sPYU1gA3mHT6SY_2kWVR4mEn2zcR9dtKExSn7BLC2oPSe_Dx4livPZk3_hEPguu5RSeJieK2_fv1s1l7Pdx9lqfXG7BjY1cLGI5dQChb_CX9q8WW9c6CmRrd3VN9OrFTOtPLjfTQLGrVrWDGeNJbVkL6_Jfu4QmYewCMj1dZBGtZuafIxM-5VIb7s8SZbRh5wNr7xCEaMuflOJDcoFCh1qpJH1CFpbixPWv7EDyjRKRKQg5Lk5v9Re8R9EPdw9WZJuw1t03yuqLQnozuH-I0m8RysKOBd_4apDu8kHIqRcGsxJuNEc8BtLI_TelkO0NhsDNg25-yaYnP4QzB4r352fORQ4FFm6THGSEOvYrR4fuRLzjPlCESr0N5JpSg_X0nYVJ6ab28jcKqCHgNJqdIvSNmM5MGOuHTDluDvW_Cu0VBaD96Y9qRVXcRErmXzYRde_V_tHyE165O-dnm2Ju" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.3B0_0a77HY/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.3B0_0a77HY/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; 1 月 12 日，洛杉矶曼德维尔峡谷地区帕利塞兹火灾后，消防队员在烧毁的山坡上&lt;i&gt;。摄影师：Kyle Grillot/Bloomberg&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;值得你花时间&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;加州政界人士正忙于让居民更容易重建在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=1b20d78946fe438a9ac466a4e85f1974&amp;amp;_e=PU2eBGaYg-XqhBpqH_rEUBtsuT3l4h6xBXd6rQ1RDLLWz7-64mpwGzQuazHvhgwC4KIKXgIDtXhzbNvdxe-E6ABAZ9avR2pfxPrFDS-9-DaUMFsKkTBZ-X6jfanJYmwsBB1cTlrDzkzDCG504y3nO05LDyM_XXF2DToElklKNlwisneV252h0miFo59eAfYfXGoB4_1MPVUlNc6kjm1GltNaAJh1kwZcIJpRmct-lYeixNDwK46KRoZmHp5t9xOyGeANz017F5InrtCsQY-5lluWhHnkxtM-ZVyj0JoMy58lJ9-_SO52C-ylCJepkNa1YSgAs3N7mP_rLNXtQE3tO44lQpOteyAAI7iTukUm84V81p96-ddIHi5AuSzRu6bK9d1W7wi-bf2B50oGE4akgdNmuHGMC4QoNWQty8TsrkIRJtfm95o4mmwmdRVSW70FQkHJ7pqVQ8LCP-jrBXuGDGx6AE1z_SQjQ8hsAEN5NphN-OS0c8rnwTvuBTGVt5UG2w05C_7ToV9KuKOtPkRWEtlWTbRyotKG-wFzlurstNJAcwZesmy5Xi_uHc8TV05gAKUms6UX3SGTSUh7Qd7taIUh977_j6Xy42rLEQma_TKpmVF21BUa8ypbWicHbDpJOmOMF0ZRxQ2rxpi7950cU7DYdzsRWv2ZYoHSAcERyI4mhKUeubE1uAQEbNTk3ATeny_BR5uV5hI6G-18UqnOBEFK3YwiO7YWoGn4wea5VT2Eq6FZELzbYx0_lfBN4K8kgDXFN_srRvk8I1AxjMR2lfZuMa7glzhGvcRh_6z_mO-sfcLpK0qELiJQBv4XQbHb-Ynz4qa5HZb_um3p8PBCpRkEiSn-13t7GYfEb9vM9tM%3D" target="_blank"&gt;洛杉矶大火&lt;/a&gt;中被烧毁的房屋。这意味着放弃旨在应对气候变化的绿色建筑指令——气候变化使气候变得更加炎热和干燥，从而引发了这样的大火——以及暂停环境审查并承诺加快审批速度。专家表示，对速度的需求必须与加强野火防御相平衡，因为随着气候影响的加剧，野火将不可避免地再次燃烧。详细了解南加州快速重建&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=1b20d78946fe438a9ac466a4e85f1974&amp;amp;_e=PU2eBGaYg-XqhBpqH_rEUBtsuT3l4h6xBXd6rQ1RDLLWz7-64mpwGzQuazHvhgwC4KIKXgIDtXhzbNvdxe-E6ABAZ9avR2pfxPrFDS-9-DaUMFsKkTBZ-X6jfanJYmwsBB1cTlrDzkzDCG504y3nO05LDyM_XXF2DToElklKNlwisneV252h0miFo59eAfYfXGoB4_1MPVUlNc6kjm1GltNaAJh1kwZcIJpRmct-lYeixNDwK46KRoZmHp5t9xOyGeANz017F5InrtCsQY-5lluWhHnkxtM-ZVyj0JoMy58lJ9-_SO52C-ylCJepkNa15xcrAEiiIHexMif65tCaxopWR1DEA3d4Yhm-jekqcabtTZaSz_GsdYUvLyt6pSttVD7sycL4TtigJPRhVF568KeBJQrQ6nrGv8nbP6xCPAI7dZHj-I2uJuf-SIY1mTg938adKzfbdQw9SUShbnjO7FY9Cqo