f; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;可以肯定的是，南非国内生产总值如此小幅增长还不足以解决世界上失业率最高的国家之一的问题。然而，它会清除国家的人口扩张速度（只是刚刚），并与劳动力市场规模的增长相匹配。这突显了南非在过去十年中所取得的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=c96be254305341618043e168e214dbe5&amp;amp;_e=DBPwY2SjV5sz1hH-KCh0oDRHNG6505XsqZW_qUZj5GqrJhOUTobpgrzzFs1m0yC6f-8M8Ge5t0jQUMsXSrYbkMPldvvx0gJKds54gs4m4Vj5MOGgUYchUhgR6l6tkvtGMdEcHqL7wTwruGD04d1UU6Bx88UWUe30TYvVxASWkBBLXlnoV-hEiNP57NHmbC3Uk_exdXndxvbKxWvHIFto0549SMZbv2LfanKCbpKI-GdiFd2TM3UQm8L8K5HYoVUutXyHyOJ-HfF9h8JX7K9J6_Ch56RUuxQ8Se50wBbZy7d_-X1TegtxnYhfUFLij8OBFP3d_yqw-h245uvpxwAZ34xf0-VQBjIerv32zvYY8ML9bv-JVTfu9ZjS1vcaGqaAJC9sZwhaOhJSUosc1FdcU70EcxkSCvrIvyjHuEkt_2wyYWKxa8zDA5x54mk_jgLYh_SNHrBuoeZPLF8VVP7Tn8J1mJdAezqP8mq48s6Bk5kVR3i04rE0nudiMfY8DRVaO_boP0eE5RsNNehk9LH6Xc5MKStYYwQnTbQUuB73YofCkDHeVHFbg0xZTImUbkV6GWKKFPr6xm6abgOrWsN-PBb0BkMx1Xv5TEEn3MHeb79BqJu_kvf7r7BQn0ZO0GE-LgqW9PxKhwLS8PkYqYPos4sThlIvwArCeQ86bkc9hhFXEGyDy4SYubrXXEJos3NNUWzzAm5O0O7C9FZY9ARWsO_RZ48ddEWLpE1rXkqqVrCneFvoxdSo45GvQtLai0Ig9ZrA63yCaylDdXwoLTgLtMD_3SIzOe7-u3vDm1QNdR9ZtCpQ2SQH5O8ZWCXPTW4u" target="_blank"&gt;悲惨记录&lt;/a&gt;。但无论如何，好消息就是好消息。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;势头转变的关键是去年五月全国选举后迅速组建的广泛联合政府引发的情绪提振。统治南非30年的非洲人国民大会毫无争议地放弃了多数席位，开启了国家政治的新时代。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;由此产生的政府将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=c96be254305341618043e168e214dbe5&amp;amp;_e=DBPwY2SjV5sz1hH-KCh0oDRHNG6505XsqZW_qUZj5GqrJhOUTobpgrzzFs1m0yC6_dhPpUi-9Sv9kcCLqDnuyYoPAVpleqkkwRPc3btoz_sMbPbyZoauoliW8Jb-MfQqx0SktrJi_o0zGRpSKJX7GMiPT55azJagm5Yc5LhIu_04rV8nv01Rh8llWfzIaBBg3mV0UdaQI7JyMvfz43sdXsh7CAucEDjoPwaqJqpSMbXMNn3NwgqhSxoWY0h23WgB8yvnOxEsRdXNyjho4M48ciMairoK24uxyyfX9rU5nnz59QJscdSci7y5qAIIYl0J3RM3SaKdRMXkX6dfMBOXRitQPRWL6VTSVv3Iw-9MQNhlbMFJDJZ_tMyZ562a6K6vO25cvSvMulyQdOJQKU9XGHjP8hy_2taY9rN_7eIMyAvAY14veF1TUENEgA25ln9NcGFNoQ316WCDVLJHO4R_cHMol_ZaF0LiGgzTRvYhYL9W_R4kdVk3eA9FIbztQuzAMyQc1ql61pDbq1Xsz27gXgc8XqrqHx4fVlJUUyb1zmMBOS3jetoctsydS4a7nHD3IaFu74IwudD7JQmY7aE52HNTQ2geJrzdVNp9fCzoUgQVlNASCimhtMabW3vNLN2MwZqUAFik4AWnsmKwJtt-83DH-gp4WkNjkWsEhta5anEjHTXr-exrZsmBHyv4fOqEY0sSuXKiK3vmu9JXrF0bKXtM9lAGXfzscTPsU7ihPmrJLiRV51ut8EBmCebmJeISYn92AY1m73uxVdmwz0VgwksscQGnX1oNl3MPNtVwNXa_U68hAePvaOaeCq-uKXaG" target="_blank"&gt;亲商的&lt;/a&gt;民主联盟（美国为数不多的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=c96be254305341618043e168e214dbe5&amp;amp;_e=DBPwY2SjV5sz1hH-KCh0oPxWMBIz9ktCKsslVdWSPeckhpCdWd0HzvJYu3zW2bM7HHyXAa12swSI9pZVhIpslqARoRVlA3Jn-Hgw75hj-XzlBCFFLAtlKoyRSHuA_OdUKgx1Pi1MNYs0x8p1SPeMo4HAV3Q_YAAvqk5KEariPrXdtw6zErnPeuoGTpRTEPen0---Rwr1NNWurCpfe2r8gXbwpYA64nDOIFb1OGl9ujUkPF4wpZk2iiKdmKRmCrvff595UIc_nWAfwGBLHU58W7rB7Zd4ILeB1KaqVxp0zDOZe4q28IUGtVEtH_OWXCnhFkWHubQazhPigvfs3CPwklaFoq7UiT2BMmuFN3Zjs0D3AT5JYaw7joj0hp_eUduJTP7-GLcbwiPtq5TDFJjkw6enmMVzLCj7ezCuAr1ywPZExgn4iHCa4q8ujMDYa5mA3vQV1CvkQmsoNZkeVh4pQeQis_-MMLGZUOP4PTBOW1Rs129w2QmF_OAGVMt1tck2Xl6qiUIKdXs7vm4TjHzhtB5hLofw95vnq5SB3OL_imQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;白人领导的政党&lt;/a&gt;之一）纳入其第二大成员。对于一个永远以白人少数民族实施的种族隔离恐怖为标志的国家来说，这个联盟是一场&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=c96be254305341618043e168e214dbe5&amp;amp;_e=DBPwY2SjV5sz1hH-KCh0oDRHNG6505XsqZW_qUZj5GqrJhOUTobpgrzzFs1m0yC6e5ttRhgO-hcxqK5JAlsyV43diWrTMf36C5HfUYbKU0mAR6hhA6g6MEOlGSo20j9Gt4M3W9mlRUuwECSauFxHveRxDhyj5TKo-aq0uXxS6cpWY1pnRxYITVjbB9RG69uiWFEPhI-ehQPIEtL9tB5ttkSs_m2x_YI4Y7cY4YUoX7Sy4SYzOtIQO45JPyOl75Q3NiGjdGVz-2bm8UAiZpslwQfYtjOpzWFXO51OOMaTPPUV8AWjf-hhOz2wsqqca4Vl_rF0k1hmhkVSon47uNwEc4ZLrQjUgIpWdRcM74rLgnNKbwQ1J6R5wVkSyYt4dsO3ov2vaWMci27NBYGeF2CiijVgOII9jEshoQOIhfE3kPzH-vHI-5D4-N2ndM9uoOimh0xC_RkWM_NdBp-Cs6jLIHqPcPjYFJJ0ax58PZHP125IFzSmMF8eI7GKjmXibgCxjD-C2_ca4f4t5O2GsgcEFVgiB3FoCbFOrJEjrUQXNb0i4gz6IDzLHLnv0yQfo3Hc6bh86MtJD2Td5DEOBxileRDnXRvaCGxUeE5vwLIT-FbGsDjELp5gJzmopoOPGohSozCurbKfHh66dObOp991p_tUFtWzfFZ58mou0xkcCd6hUVjVPv6wtHYbFU-n6CxKd1tg9k2arLOmFmPeOnnGbPZwkyx9YChRcQ_Ywilbakr43LcgabzJ8jiVU4v1uVfqMp0Y87_eIOEzaEv7YAAcogDhcd8GY_e6qShjVmid5W8%3D" target="_blank"&gt;政治地震&lt;/a&gt;。但这也标志着非国大传统上国家参与经济倾向的转变。由于一家国家航空公司刚刚摆脱破产，国家权力和物流公用事业几乎破产，共产党对商业部门表现出了新的开放态度。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;但复苏是脆弱的，2025 年可能会决定复苏能否持续。有些事情超出了政府的控制范围。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiGD6L._0C28/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiGD6L._0C28/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;约翰内斯堡郊外斯泰恩市的公寓楼。这里遍布人造泻湖、自行车道和餐馆，房屋售价高达 5000 万兰特（270 万美元），象征着南非严重的财富不平等。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Cebisile Mbonani/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;11 月的美国大选也有力地重塑了全球环境，对即将上任的特朗普政府政策的担忧&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=c96be254305341618043e168e214dbe5&amp;amp;_e=DBPwY2SjV5sz1hH-KCh0oDRHNG6505XsqZW_qUZj5GqrJhOUTobpgrzzFs1m0yC6TA4b8GYH_lQKQCyNHGlAJ8d7ePPQiIuT1sHuaLgkVfPeyoQ4veDl7YcT4sWr5B-90CcREC-EFo-1doaQT2nyDTnpMrmgpdPAVvC16IdtwrOE8nG3HA2254DtqqzcztFHzYyU1pkPBQAD6bi9Mh6wgUoirS8Sup4KHLLpf0Zo4IIraGVyvKDz0HPqOXeOxG6-xWQIK--fomZ4W86qcIFAUvrNNklkSFbftDpeYTLGFPWp30jiRV3TvnwEck_eYPL8mEIum-w3ukIq32N523qEE3NVM8evrNf3HP03b8nUOpVJMm2G9VKXcKCIPCu5ZYrA6egeYPQrjkYvEauEB4Veh1Ddk_dFPSejVVdOCz4bZNfKN0b9fEFkh_1ChG2odj9ZMxfHWOzNGugRmp0m-agMcBuoSvfdXjxA5K_h6q9XWP5EnT3URKyeqvvEmykw6kicfk63YHxt5t8l6xU6una3I7do46Mbd2UvB0yY4Jm8M1EGLVepxkEyYT962BSvhJYB3KMOAAZGoOq4tpasP0mayN_35a4pl6apWxwqPm5iNnVslE8gg-7pEwErbGR594XqahCkcr1rBvwcjXOHscv_xCgL2Ctb4OLQUBwaath-f7fiu9fXUuTr0E9kca2j7ibCURmvC1GSafBrf3TAHVaXydkEjQhPdmpHGl7BURMfCPPXf9qaLg0GGN_GTBs7hbW58pqb4fh-5vMVUmjzm6wXpnySCBy3d4-KRYy-bKk3Pl8%3D" target="_blank"&gt;推动美元&lt;/a&gt;走高，包括兑兰特。这反过来又削弱了南非&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=c96be254305341618043e168e214dbe5&amp;amp;_e=DBPwY2SjV5sz1hH-KCh0oDRHNG6505XsqZW_qUZj5GqrJhOUTobpgrzzFs1m0yC66vzdjXllyI_Bsa1jLTvn6-rYAc0QWYeRFdiGg_WfPjF_shcbPDT54Y-72kDuKhumNc4RAgjm7mVIuq2CRjBz1vCHvq5rc_kJxfqqOTQhMK7CYmMZg1zFOW5UahVB4T8gjCop-tazVVJ0kmk2qaYAD7S28Zjn5GQA5yW_t7JR0KWjjtG46vfq_8CANEok8uh5ILFSkcOk5m7RbC_IjQTrElNWgHG4zZrqMP7wTvbEa4r-jlcPnsONH-2LFHKl6NenyUGdV51-79MTNG3pwkjfLP33oVnW-LqpLl6ddl12ODnbkUdVlJVJho4Z01VICCghrr2SiMH5QMkAxxKQp_a24Y8UqyKwdJUTXz-wFXIWyzA2Evk4e949P-X5gT-ovZMdb9l9D0AEwpACzEluw73bcV9UDyLLG53a7cadqdKrhV5g3zBFhvgSatgEBl3v7M7yWZHQ7cHwQ9bU4LDOO4ZE8g0KgsLvnhU3ZtFtpwwgPV6cJ7jtilShWNAkYaR03xqvn7WxUXVFWhgl9KrrblltkxDIrVrsjUG_W_v0YL78mw2J9O-hgUrHF2F4e2V2Otx-MwU8wEnemMhAUNwklEPb-SeyLscZkC_bDVj2qsW4Kess_O63MIISGdW_iIJHiO3mhErVwm0suqEt22nDdJ7Qf_7iELagbBCeWjp5UbfSr3c2VlM6iY0pcO5ieKRhgh4PAAckE8yikXxMUgShK-gbx-4OnAle3rKMb1Mmt8ZUBTmwhdAfisdpm6fzO839d11u" target="_blank"&gt;降低利率&lt;/a&gt;的能力，否则南非本来可以提振经济增长。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;为了让南非有最好的机会维持经济发展势头，新的联盟可能需要保持完整， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=c96be254305341618043e168e214dbe5&amp;amp;_e=DBPwY2SjV5sz1hH-KCh0oDRHNG6505XsqZW_qUZj5GqrJhOUTobpgrzzFs1m0yC6Iwpw3AcIcCI35awK6gzP2ZRrBh86ZhR2ugc3UJyOfxzbvhuDkh0pTpl7qy2QZ6J3Psgovx0o0fprpMDzAiVqrGldDOp4dPoPvRh3VNfJQOcycp1oYt-Fv6FACbQjzPpSOBu3xHhZa2tbEvBrc2KlRGwVZMcH_lCWKfITC4TJLiMde-ZsmTXVAo11mrgjhSmNPlEVNGcLDh4cvNugtnrrDogunYeGaZ_sbhyV0hCpK8iCTsh8ZE4cWacvZX10y5WhBC4s5qbyr7NKE_WQZzQfCmHdSaM0W3Hz2dW1Zj8vtAX9tjMC_Mu1YEa2QW9Fp-YPFokBKPtE2tNmXFnWV_8YynTZY_phlZ6foXz_aE1Qcq1oNF_u8Xo97QqzrPZ_nUjc3BJYiK4F0c-i2BJK3VaegYx4D