mily: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;以色列和加沙的下一步是什么？&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a624c521bcac40ae9091ca274aea884e&amp;amp;_e=YTSh-CylcCkim7SjOWkISGimBFojKxxQld4j0GuUaJZZrKQryLil0LDE0p_zXNoN_bhHZ0-5h8KJ0mV0FQE7QdYse95O54tXz2kjbbA9TRppyf3Ad0elUmEFw2Xf5bK-V4r9Vm5os3oqn5BbUgqFatkDkndZTpDPeHalRYFMfHman-IGhIngwQyPcSdnqkt_gUT7SnIMUM0a6mcRh_cd2RuIYJw5Df4v9E1xk9MHFszEN2I6WrJSZQr3QoiLP33GRETkMWK-vdfiW5Iq4W3XcaLihZRioFGTaWe3K8r-eIpVrtHWRysUPT4xuMnr52v4p09DFcOl2YLoPG9bHScbqH55_6E9ML88kkI_-9MYw3ahSoyiigGOUSlQG2ErVRAvicvbkDQcpuz1p1ET44ycItp_yrdeitD5R5ocmKK_1FkLhKJdG3peZveUHovz17H6iJk5fZD5odEbHNXU5Qqpk2chjRryYvwJOGstH05Wvt4%3D"&gt;停火协议&lt;/a&gt;是结束战争的第一步，但唯一达成一致的部分将在短短六周内结束。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;为什么这些房屋能够抵御洛杉矶大火？&lt;/strong&gt;在被毁坏的街区，一些房屋仍然矗立。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a624c521bcac40ae9091ca274aea884e&amp;amp;_e=YTSh-CylcCkim7SjOWkISGimBFojKxxQld4j0GuUaJaFjKOYCf9Zn_MA1crhB4xZdywP8GXAb5Wb9jgptayhZoLPuOPiD9fhm6GCXuW0DvqYVb9zt0V0RFZIedVymM8WqmGnYcJiax6Gbc3RhyDZHBcTw0OOZRholoO55Xvnfi4e1QWvgJ14IysIeGCqnYwul3Yfu7vhD5prNV7sAU15BsK845u0hp-k0P-IOU9zip4SdupkepFQU-9Iev1aRgywvviX3pot4SWlDaTp6eFcYDZl95FRj6P6Tulf_7jp0p2NuZ1h-WKhjvZN1xwcMHhYdhDeApPNi7duREENE0q-iZ96vxCLJXt8_9WvEkmLYpLpKEVWYYyuMJdL8fxx4NPEH6HeEzec7LyUVX_biRfjCDkBJSrCTHHX8LKX5vSWLUpv7N7DLG_UEe-3HbaChHHS3jJeBPvOrt1dXSAvQEx0wA%3D%3D"&gt;建筑师在本周的头条新闻中解释了原因&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;对于就职典礼来说，多冷算太冷？&lt;/strong&gt;罗纳德·里根的第二次仪式是有史以来最冷的，但&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a624c521bcac40ae9091ca274aea884e&amp;amp;_e=YTSh-CylcCkim7SjOWkISGimBFojKxxQld4j0GuUaJaFjKOYCf9Zn_MA1crhB4xZL7uXiVp5A37tzZJFLRr-danLtyioWp6dVsIiQO_d6IcZwwjBz_XGXaSl2b_4Yw653g3uWHT0o4icFqQIOxdTwJleI2_RINqgEYDdkBsNyJ6y4icclg-TeKt77qtgCxpQ4h19pAz8uJeRzMbroerExDzG7tjNaCxtZuQ4gQ6V0snpx5E84QOeRuyhC7tTPTPx0-45K1ZPKeW7nYMhmBhiwsx_5UwOO4BzrU-OKggE_SYFa36eeuJ3sok7J7gNButMnPr1647llEyI8NGSW4PRwEMR1msV7A0NHMNIGaq2GCU0oBcPPjgJkdZ9akPzGy-umFgqzs7D49TlctdOPU_yqrrC4XVHmUbFzt-9eV3avnCO50ULSyeMmCXC-7Ob2Z2UNaPDsRu6QN6o0gyElWRt4A%3D%3D"&gt;特朗普的仪式将在&lt;/a&gt;上面——呃，下面——那里。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;CEO周末做什么？&lt;/strong&gt;从风筝冲浪到有声读物狂欢，再到在体育运动中击败孩子，九位高管&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a624c521bcac40ae9091ca274aea884e&amp;amp;_e=YTSh-CylcCkim7SjOWkISGimBFojKxxQld4j0GuUaJaFjKOYCf9Zn_MA1crhB4xZbkyU_jgYrrYeAaCmQFNRw1uhOwkwGw0a0GVdXe8wrzw7zJiQjLU4BLBY2ISWlEr9RmiFM6JlfZKUPuTOiU1YqEfhN0cbxbKqkIJ83cZsrSfk7PBUx4WBoW_wMPrilLsty07DaQJ1en2xcBGqG-NldDUR7BLQ6Y5IS7EpRjssDTXZnFXX4H1vCOwuuhc2zGoVcUbbt5ZzMyqbEiB1vWolbooKKYlPpV4ts8rWrvDDutc5F-tN6PoO6R5cw0Pffzfqcnat45Tbx9dvJuHoBGJ6q1g7uuMHgsmKqF3nvYXEA1Wkc5WvlAC6Qu-runppzK_tTMQjq7XDXqovH7Jm_waJtitV7BXtH5NUDd84pXig_hnbpcfwO8vkKZntOx9qsPTfT60oIZoBMUDqwV_mwM42DA%3D%3D"&gt;告诉我们他们喜欢如何放松&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;您可以在线或在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a624c521bcac40ae9091ca274aea884e&amp;amp;_e=YTSh-CylcCkim7SjOWkISGimBFojKxxQld4j0GuUaJYAbX11gnUtieRgeXAj0If3n6AkfgBkt542BmRTnPMOTT6CQm6KX7ZK-vjweaTmBsBw-S4EDhioP1bt2dsTNXKHc9NVzT0ZpmfdQ6zMAKUkyF295TF2hDCc4k3jSAe9Ug1elPku1n0kH1HQzRI_JEVRjneg8qnFe67WJt5wrLccLQ