制作的金砖，顾客可以在里面享受米其林星级厨师的甜点。这只是全球最大的奢侈品牌在中国销量下滑之际将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a624c521bcac40ae9091ca274aea884e&amp;amp;_e=YTSh-CylcCkim7SjOWkISGimBFojKxxQld4j0GuUaJZZrKQryLil0LDE0p_zXNoNLRZHduf6lx59F_VlI_VPmohfG-lNmRnACkAnW_letx0x1cTdiY-R34cNUbfJH1KGklJQ5n1RnmQbKsgX04mU-7UpUo_ApS98fE7CvvytoXrUvuJHNY2X_pDWvJvc8w-KNRo0dh9ScLUxt36iMLi1nmlts_7XAeAejQfjC0PU2Upf6-ki7KDqqcxwTrhhJFfQ32r7_0ZhPd5egxeh1oGqH56fmtIp_dglhapaG0uvjI7MfZ3jB3Hw_gLQlTUKunFBTI31kojVFb33NW-xPnftM95HBVemhWwVoIjzB1UxZgcYx-sFE7giPwCV5p_bNphFiWYs5e_geN_-huu5jsdc0LLONXPQN7JkANyb4iZW3GYAG0nzaRmNCCzItuwUBaWRMR4PqCtpdaJixEeKCVnxDqU144n8woStGzuSq2FxXnY%3D"&gt;注意力转向泰国&lt;/a&gt;的一个例子。&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=a624c521bcac40ae9091ca274aea884e&amp;amp;_e=YTSh-CylcCkim7SjOWkISGimBFojKxxQld4j0GuUaJZZrKQryLil0LDE0p_zXNoNLRZHduf6lx59F_VlI_VPmohfG-lNmRnACkAnW_letx0x1cTdiY-R34cNUbfJH1KGklJQ5n1RnmQbKsgX04mU-7UpUo_ApS98fE7CvvytoXrUvuJHNY2X_pDWvJvc8w-KNRo0dh9ScLUxt36iMLi1nmlts_7XAeAejQfjC0PU2Upf6-ki7KDqqcxwTrhhJFfQ32r7_0ZhPd5egxeh1oGqH56fmtIp_dglhapaG0uvjI42RbJXKpSbS1cjK79bQS9Me6KxB2IoqfUaLJwCiCSg_oKqe_toVz1KRSXvtUhM92m7ZD418iVyur05F6Jog7bAIuhz8NTrJhRIkP2yo0an-Y9q5USZYXE6r1ny-ouRVP5ZBD1QtmlRUUi1JM8s5MKs3tVwLUjy4b91UgHLTZCpAfifr_SUtcqYabho-Ne7FmQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="The Dior store in Bangkok" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3xffqc9lwBQ/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="曼谷迪奥专卖店" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3xffqc9lwBQ/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso