员健康福利基金的金额的额外投资。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;她写道：“非常措施可能持续的时间存在很大的不确定性，包括预测美国政府未来几个月的付款和收入的挑战。”尽管共和党人将于周一控制联邦政府的所有部门， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5b45b38c3f124f3c8a9abb9db7542492&amp;amp;_e=6PpeAQ4JXCf2kdBycWtWxM-Nk9xFANzQnNeRCz8uDxfWXLjSYOmCJsAJbkDJCq1ivSfkUzMLZSxAR_2X4EaPmjBsrxz2S6iFj7cImScPKKGqJS2oOg4c0PSeqgIbpLSTcu0gxALlUR7RUkoUucuIe0p6zd7CeiM9Hi4VHA4IRwfvu48kIdl4EJi7fypa_ixrmLozk3ZJUwC2-FAPDYEaikg_tPArtLYL0fQ4EKbL7AxGS1S2s802i2Dw8gnHLHCye7_kbkG6dHNn5Pa9OkDq1UcvW-KUSvy3HjzkMo6BIT_LsxhFMyCWO0RUwUWLopTo_Su6M08D1C6OFO6_Jcsej03IhmFrwuqF5nIiN_znNbGqXrNxSQnu2TmYAhX2Dqknnlti7g05wQbfHIRzROfBt978n6hMCiirkA5yxZRThr4ccr4zrYD2CMxcWqwtAZvC_VD_Soko7RPW6JwA4cYM2RLEr9TnW9yHt4xNJaMzJODzWVL4WExflC36ksTE-cxnX2LBfQOIKeqeVJ9D4-I538M62PzRpe2JnJr1x4LOZOPWtJbg0kOHmJD1iObnvmIAnnegwgps7lYyg2qgW7qkTAanCHHmlqGRQLvr1ahRm-K_NMLFGLwmi-0GALQ24g2Gb7IiPr1XvOryC7iU_ze6n0cOBiEErvFDKOpSDjnkttHhr7fEQon5zepozfnN-LImRhML9iO2ze7acF7VSN-lhQt5OAS58SSVGkc69e_OxH3Ee7kOjkdZDxH5FQ4ttZcD" target="_blank"&gt;但不一定能保证&lt;/a&gt;达成协议以避免灾难。那限制呢？这是 36 万亿美元。 &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;— &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5b45b38c3f124f3c8a9abb9db7542492&amp;amp;_e=6PpeAQ4JXCf2kdBycWtWxM-Nk9xFANzQnNeRCz8uDxeKVycJC5jP6GlkcoA-EkrhcrdQLiNp4WQ3RBVPxIAFdRUG7BmDZCCS8ZhM1Y4xdlM7cmEGLcLou6DISw8uMqdO-tF6vbtRLTZAfJonDXWBIGW9oBEeFBxj2fA7TFoDNnx1zlecWklEDNuBEtJ-Wmrdh5OyeRmzcEbDINv62rLuz7Mgmb8Y2_xYRx2OTcLwaJeV_0Dva5Hd1zChx3Vbcj5tYJoG0XxYxFveQvYDSR0Ja6lr9ybyNjMrSDsxaon79a4SxFgTsfHxU3ynIwZu6pQLyq0sWIErX_ioTwmrWsGtS8Za0mrfRUX2dMaLLVKb5CP4qhqnYDd-yWk8Jtu4ehLLSpn712vcwlFSdKtq-0Vp3z3uAucaoWmwZHjoV-ZHMH-EfP-Eqb_c8b2hveNiQn4jVbLuesuvdJu1jJwtikqtCA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;大卫·E·罗维拉&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;tab