t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SZVOnttnBAnbE4g8eXiHjNAzbyS2_WW1AOFBOLola8fUMEzQDekEtsgy82MJ-pj6RXmByxzZwMrySwbKe3yYHZjy4tNSNCktL0s9XekrkLz_ev-Vmd9JWSfY4aSvSgFtYnOHf5L_hOFRALjxiEtwHdgOKfyIH-bgtYozgTE21qdk55UNovc29xFoEYX_rVcbufx-FQfkkdZhEjMNO6_8qWx47YXgNvxA9IuvR3NqFGvVLRK9vS2V4tVV2fH0ozSOal7pHFuE9zbQ6T58lVVoj5R6iZLNZvFNmeL-BgILSe75c7U6XOHoAv0Wtl-BpLuvzA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;指责哈马斯违背了&lt;/a&gt;一些承诺，这项&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SQBwqXLFAtBrJzSwWXsP_UaZGWIAOEQp51uGL_fQFp9rY9VXLvrSxizwfSkrEjdEVnb6C-71SbSs1adgjpGUAWkiJacVkVFcHqke6FOrEaOofMLahWo48GCwLcPUddl3CkL05dvQNx6Ly90I-utL04WJrRVvMJGMyavu47VD8rc1RSwFKj8NKtsqY6uaAXQVF4ncqDyOEtbPcIoC-keDxcUvGNIDh53FDDM54NqueMZ_2ZarPPfRFS_wz-HEyD85b5hamBu1MBfz97X2CMoN__-tOrf9MGXK4tQ-8VsrcouIJOuzYXjZep7K2R-nnstacw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;期待已久的协议&lt;/a&gt;看起来有破裂的风险。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;据《华尔街日报》报道，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普已经准备了&lt;/strong&gt;约 100 项行政命令，他的目标是在周一就职典礼后迅速采取行动。知情人士称，其中一项命令&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SSVc8sEEEbaSYM-H2nwqr-CGlJCzyPo9uK9h-5is7Jup-boK_fOdUDorgxrOOgPDb6fKn9lURyz--krtHqBCqlffIcumLYPkokoijtg4mQusZGth0hTPiXG0jBg7Jrr-Ax2J7kBVraYkkiyoAaUjr22zodd10RajLBi56O3CgUnQh__ODpHE_cpCfWxc0OAJYliPBtjuEeQeoTjIc0aF1ZIpG2yJiTz6sh84sJyw1hPalmGmTCFgsNGE8V2aJnwlpmU-mtMocsK8F_7QAdol3B-s2TxyIXMJCB-ExGgTHBFUXq1F0EePjsPP0ZVON6fANw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将加密货币提升为政策优先事项&lt;/a&gt;，并让业内人士在其政府中拥有发言权。这无疑会让今晚在华盛顿举行的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SbnL9uwZmG0BwYlMWS5KWpPNJAH4hunlljuVq3LhmFKFIemkA5ADGV507dAqnHRVSSbx_dtMCKGXP5P0Key-T4qSSE68gxwKo47R1f9ESJw5NPMRThBR58GO_GrtUcgePTR91gIRIDzBFrWywKOLWWi7YNOJvSepdSQfryQiYIDMRSOjr7SSGWf9PipZaFyWcZhh6Z5Xv_u8IP83nEl-N9XfydXipi0Ej5oyokqqbmLaUFf3fqmamqkiCkqhtNdSv2r2YJAxwP9hUZSFeDDpKNWhXQ4x23wYg8pvxkuni43cK1xqjLq_PUQFPIA-IJaZ7Q%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;每张门票 2,500 美元的加密舞会&lt;/a&gt;更加热闹，这是一个为纪念这位&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6Sd_D4dDKJ9c8nXOv2XnWFRoyWvej8RtydStCrOdQ_YZkawF92_sw9WJrYB02trWbjAxWZ46aahyBQJ2oHKEyep227jWjA8inAW9y5GKW3YhC_mv2PuIrW0r4tJcB2iKNECjHCCscRsVyLoH9bgbEKG3gisiA5nJYm4OeLAxWtJqY4dQ5NbGN8iGFr02R1YSuW6lpU3JjP1kO01Tw2zk_exQXM6A2bx7oPEoUIYZyNyAZ_C8mxp-rn8FZ7PH9ExXC_dQtWaEaJ6nqM5PBVOgxqmSwVPtRHa5mLwE2l3IcbmFpRJTOhdvoWXHDDyQ8UO87nw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;数字货币怀疑论者摇身一变的拉拉&lt;/a&gt;队长当选总统而举办的大型派对。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在洛杉矶，由于有毒锂增加了危险材料的混合物，燃烧的电动汽车&lt;/strong&gt;和家用电池存储系统使毁灭性野火后的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SUgcmUIS5BmN0ugtRsi1YbHwQOezeNQTl4Cd7z8cyYVR3ltRSZaR8AbvFT68QwNaH5tipFXJOvx-QS_5VCmzy9EoJ5LIq6j_7DsW9JCDoqKxFJVrX-CYievhcMru3VSUw7JHczzpvF0MDu_r1QAEnZet4k7nwp4s-0So6ovI7FvRp1x8IK3bPG7j2ZscjBSToaRD1Q9FlZFBXBQBNOYB3n4tVTdf9GqAlLQXV4LWB0M40IU5zO7VYjqotdTnegwJDCEJ0DQwlGQtNzN42R_vcgr14pN0TV94GfkbbRab5hmOCHuReJvj6zDxrkK2gmYg4w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;清理工作变得更加复杂&lt;/a&gt;。一夜之间，世界上最大的电池存储设施之一&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SdsbErp8kA9E2y4haw6Im6NwamRzBuPpfX68qi2zxKsoRK74jn9_ORcdLaln7VsdD6GvhbtHrndiJrauPS372gce9nwEbf4vWwIlAQIFkWA9ti5PGEMHq4lFGLTv88RBpXmFPj0MJRbuGE1wvzHTyk0UI61gwY2TVhoEE3552rn88jwu-TT6xR48sHXM4b5YW4_6ByxvT3LgEwSvr76zD5Eag43RGGo3udsCibUuLHh4hdn-j8Gozt56SzXcsTsXyEtBgQpy-X11OzjkkaJ2zXvqahyCJfiYPFR9vpyahAXBRp69O5yJgW8Jvk-5SS3GmA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;又发生火灾&lt;/a&gt;。与此同时，为了支持恢复工作，一场&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6STFIZcJXC-VKpl3JkoQ_yLL-bPyHqPwBvGvFhQ1iZvpvAaeynLLE4Mf8JNeyltKuAc9QdBJeeI8q5bfkbwHEqW2WPLIe-0A2Yj9zU-pGhB0QCTL9G2FxnVSkt_tu8MPV8X6ycUh1-8lTOtDPv4D2w9lR47rjrVblaqEaKygSxtj0YXOXa15mU7A-5OxjD34hIa5yGGG8PxP9tTafWFG7wpVoO_KDFgZn_OOFtgbfl-5Mr-oLtsVW8nKCmy5jyemZO3cOvTo6IGjnuiBNB-J03SN17ApUcC5IEGbLoqyKk_UCQq_89mV_3OBG13M_goHoLA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;众星云集的慈善音乐会&lt;/a&gt;定于 1 月 30 日举行。音乐会将在多个流媒体服务上播出，以最大限度地为受害者提供捐款。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SckSKV3KJ7Pijr7LyyYtL39PunUCkx6Unx89gbhW8CSbKGfr3F1zIGpzpq_6rhwmmdPsTEEht87q8LtylOl9Gmj8RPcSA2xvI1ljhUpSsAY4nk7-pI9E7OVH3t_9NuxXVCyhOpjtjBqI8lclwQiTWiEYRvWS6j_2Dg1be1h3CbMvlIpAJvvhFxAmSiyQms4Hm-3SVI71RbvOqsyHGJt1M0-1WWr94B6f0mXoBdlGvBmvl9PYDXl7xdtJqnjUrJa5MQGAA5owZPZfM7kCcAzC323Ul9G9PPUghJtwjrS_m-Jkj22ecYjiq1hFZYEu3g7HnA%3D%3D" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8fU70oSHLP