a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SccL6S6sS6XWvAxseoLaresmtAtit5KZoCHXxVGsJr1JJP3eCnvLNZCIDbsZEM5uTagvOSceHwoHMxOZcxGRGStK8IIYqpmwxCKH6toMp977d0JGjRdS--YSA5EfLcArQIQl4SjadRjG6OeIMB90U-j_CMEyjPB6p_xry6lEHK7RAu0Ti3_kVSoDivmk21nx-mcW2cdtsYiJSdzJG1G_bzalD-g0H_XWViAnrqp0QEzhy-_iCKZwkGVjAFM-NRTiaommt7kdAopSgWsyh5ttZR-A-RJo9KetNxgk39QwZFQhxduk37GwYhuZPPWxreve8g%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;拥堵费的第一周成功&lt;/a&gt;打破了该市臭名昭著的交通拥堵。但不要太习惯。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;根据 MTA 数据，进入 60 街以下区域&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;的汽车数量&lt;/strong&gt;比正常水平&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SVaDc9o7dmhApeVV_9mcn6a3SVcUuRgE2QSqD4QapUTS_xtD6ycFzALs696R-ApELVcVoDCaRRar5RparOq6KbHRORuBt_o5kqk3kwQQGS0-9Xckxxh0ENUHgkD5nwvbaFWm6fkjOUpqU1bwzEeG4vwoFjJW9CjXGh-EFuzKiwx3jSYEhh1LwM5dmGtCcnrBmrptCtbXXGCvGOZKkMPySSufu9hUHYTv8iT2RujD2fdcwDx6_EoV9tx1Arg-ys3PzxEOWDZoTax9WG6VoYVMo6isZLgYtATBsqZDo82LMUaqjEt43p1tMTZTzMgAaQWP9w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;减少了约 8%&lt;/a&gt; ，而交通速度大幅提高。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;哪些车消失了？&lt;/strong&gt;现在下结论还为时过早，但我们对 75,000 辆汽车的分析发现，更快的速度很可能是由于私人车辆的减少。对于黄色出租车和其他时间就是金钱的司机来说，这是个好消息。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SccL6S6sS6XWvAxseoLarevJMSpPOydKyCcmui4HAPMGeLF7tZ4vj1qxrFWU21b6xahSVkNY4g7mW5dgqDRJHuUb10142oDdnSMESmKtmrmyE79CiZHAttQSQnk50_fiHM2jMffx6rE3r1UmF84SV1WAnK_Tv4b34GZdPFnlA6AHUoKv_m8akb3u_tlmkahjVlaxmRNUENRrt0X-xT3mg7q8dtKt9BnRv2f9fjpma1u4TWb7Rd_5-_vVSHcNZyTYI5g3WKAzEdbsSjUhB4BXjBBGThtr3O8Y7aZMgzlCnAg79zW6DICivurhIGdAJ7nTNA%3D%3D" t