雄心勃勃的火星计划遭遇挫折&lt;/a&gt;。这次事故发生在杰夫·贝佐斯的蓝色起源&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SSDz4eM8eP1wgkLGMO8ezbL5X1OqHy4HP05wX1sH4Eo6sQ5pdpV0OFXU_ey6YJTyIkpk3Hv-KUG1IcLJqcnT3_ivBIHS5H21KBI7m41nGHGOYF7HfOte9l_wgrxHuE52BGg9w0i0Ey3oFA082NwXJ4-8vJXVp1DE_-05GYZYi4VFkKu0CfFoJ6I_zaKAN1nj1tsfTC5oXV7gAZAmQSi6zTbLX_Iyfxq6twkGgd_cjPZCbo5CtGr-HOx7tiBgcAJC5MaNUtOSQa4ongXzPkvNIygNbP4qC-0mIVTJvGQ7fgTCip_NKLatFX0lf5tP1O7j9Q%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;进入轨道&lt;/a&gt;几小时后，加剧了亿万富翁之间的太空竞赛。捷蓝航空和美国航空不得不&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SYnjbUktwsp5tQTQ0Z94EfLzzR_X4xJ_YhA7MAd-uC0GpbkQejqO7TFirQCd0N1eDp59Coo0Do-lPUmU5CZ0UnH5hJQg1uV6-EglhHM9nmiNhOkPcveQiAVQzRO_lDZNr6RnuRLOR_VKVxzGjj-T0HEK6MN6MYVMBiyhEqF8G5piEB4DRmdCfPJqqytzemPhSuR3IqvujTVngZib69K0PQG-ajL8GpSysNCQ2euQ6UQN0H94d_dXFuOtzNa0O8eEA-vt5jCVUptFKgoOqSKi9xBoSuUpHv3e8u8TlgVhOQ9td65vUM6Y3fq1sCU83e0OaA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将一些飞机转移到&lt;/a&gt;加勒比海上空，以避免太空碎片。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px 8px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td colspan="2"&gt;还有一件事&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: #CCC; padding: 16px 8px 9px 0px; border: none;" valign="top" width="129"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2317965f77aa44dab4cf6c0a6504b295&amp;amp;_e=LneWFpQIw8cSW1xTKXZ6SQFN2YyYJWJF4y-dU7l6mKefMpleB9DaVI3y9w1HjYc4wmW6Pyj6PvQELJfGsGbpeY